<h2 id="syntax">Syntax</h2>
<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="s2">"typographer"</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">boolean</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="nv">$value</span> <span class="c1">// default false</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<p>Adds some useful shortcodes to make typing faster, while also provide a very limited misspell helper</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Shortcode</th>
      <th>Replacements</th>
